// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2896 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 2d514a48-3dca-5570-8678-92f26df6aebd

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
